• If you are a school employee between academic years;
• If you fail to participate in reemployment services;
• If you do not respond promptly to an inquiry from any unit within the Division;
• If you fail to contact your local office as required; or
• If you do not call the information Hotline (TeleBenefits) or do not use the internet (WebBenefits) to properly file for your weekly UI benefit payment as required.
